ructors!&lt;/b&gt; Assign &lt;i&gt;LearningCurve&lt;/i&gt; activities and watch your students and class use our adaptive quizzing to master course content.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;/div&gt; &lt;div class="lc-rw-body-copy"&gt; &lt;span&gt;Here's how it works:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;Choose which &lt;i&gt;LearningCurve&lt;/i&gt; activities you want to assign.&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Enable Student registration and enter your course information.&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Use Reports to see how your class and students are doing on &lt;i&gt;LearningCurve&lt;/i&gt; activities. &lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;To create a new course, select "Create new course" in the top banner.&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/div&gt; &lt;div class="lc-action-button"&gt;

